welcome_message_body: Welcome to Warwick, where history meets charm! Known for its picturesque streets, historic landmarks, and vibrant arts scene, we invite you to explore and enjoy all that our beautiful city has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at T. F. Green Airport serves all commercial flights and is divided into two concourses.

terminals.name: Terminal B
terminals.description: Terminal B at T. F. Green Airport serves as the international terminal and also handles some domestic flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at State Airport houses all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at State Airport handles all freight and cargo shipments.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at New Bedford Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at New Bedford Airport handles all freight and cargo shipments.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves all commercial flights and includes amenities such as restaurants, shops, and lounges.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal caters to private and chartered flights, offering exclusive services and facilities for passengers.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's complimentary wifi network for internet access.
